Question: Explain to a younger friend how to apply for a college.
Answer:
applying for college is much easier nowadays thanks to the common app. Before beginning, know that you should compile a list of your major activities and accomplishments in school. Go through the application filling in information in each field. Also know that you will need to write one or two essays based on provided proposals, as well as include one or two letters of recommendation from some of your teachers or superiors.